先把alpine.rb 放到 /usr/local/Library/Formula/alpine.rb

$ brew install alpine --with-maildir-patch --with-ldaps-patch --with-gb18030-patch --with-wrap-line-patch


或者直接

$ brew install https://github.com/scateu/alpine-patches/raw/master/brew/alpine.rb  --with-maildir-patch --with-ldaps-patch --with-gb18030-patch --with-wrap-line-patch
